---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-100 to-orange-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Kelebihan yang Membuat Bisnis Anda Selalu Unggul</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-16">Tingkatkan efisiensi dan produktivitas bisnis Anda</p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Hemat Biaya Operasional</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Kurangi biaya administrasi dan operasional dengan otomasi sistem</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tingkatkan Penjualan</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Analisis data penjualan untuk membuat keputusan bisnis yang lebih baik</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Keamanan Data Terjamin</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Data bisnis Anda tersimpan aman dengan enkripsi tingkat enterprise</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Respon Cepat</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Sistem yang ringan dan cepat untuk melayani pelanggan dengan optimal</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Mudah Digunakan</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Interface yang intuitif, tidak perlu training khusus untuk mengoperasikan</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Akses Dari Mana Saja</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Cloud-based system yang bisa diakses kapan saja, dimana saja</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
